properties.name: Calabar-Gabon Safe Corridor
properties.description:
Safe overland route from Calabar (Nigeria) to Otsala Kokowa National Park (Gabon).
Bypasses Equatorial Guinea entirely. Minimizes Anglophone Cameroon crisis zone.

**Total Distance:** 1399 km
**Estimated Drive Time:** 21 hours

**Cameroon Transit:** 914 km, ~13 hours

## Route Segments:
Calabar → Ikom: ✓ Safe
Ikom → Ekok Border: ⚡ CAUTION
Ekok Border → Mamfe: ⚠️ TRANSIT ONLY
Mamfe → Kumba: ⚠️ TRANSIT ONLY
Kumba → Douala: ✓ Safe
Douala → Edéa: ✓ Safe
Edéa → Yaoundé: ✓ Safe
Yaoundé → Mbalmayo: ✓ Safe
Mbalmayo → Ebolowa: ✓ Safe
Ebolowa → Ambam: ✓ Safe
Ambam → Kye-Ossi: ⚡ CAUTION
Kye-Ossi → Bitam: ✓ Safe
Bitam → Minvoul: ✓ Safe
Minvoul → Otsala Kokowa NP Area: ✓ Safe

## Key Safety Notes:
• **Anglophone Zone (Mamfe-Kumba):** DO NOT stop. Transit in daylight only.
• **Douala onwards:** Francophone Cameroon is safe.
• **Kye-Ossi:** Tripoint border - take the GABON crossing, not EQ Guinea.
• **Equatorial Guinea:** Completely avoided.

## When to Travel:
• Dry season (Nov-Feb) preferred
• Always travel in daylight through Anglophone zone
• Allow 3-4 days for the full crossing with rest stops

properties.name: Calabar
properties.description: Nigerian port city. Entry point. Stock up on supplies, get Cameroon visa stamped. Safe.

properties.name: Ikom
properties.description: Last major Nigerian town before border. Fill fuel tanks. Safe.

properties.name: Ekok Border
properties.description: Nigeria-Cameroon border crossing. Legitimate crossing point. Have papers ready.

properties.name: Mamfe
properties.description: ⚠️ ANGLOPHONE ZONE - DO NOT STOP. Transit only. Drive in daylight ONLY.

properties.name: Kumba
properties.description: ⚠️ ANGLOPHONE ZONE - Still dangerous. Continue to Douala. Do not stop except checkpoints.

properties.name: Douala
properties.description: Francophone Cameroon - SAFE. Major city. Rest, resupply. French-speaking zone.

properties.name: Edéa
properties.description: Safe transit town on main highway N3 to Yaoundé.

properties.name: Yaoundé
properties.description: Capital - SAFE. Good rest stop. Embassies, hotels, supplies.

properties.name: Mbalmayo
properties.description: Safe town south of Yaoundé on main route south.

properties.name: Ebolowa
properties.description: Capital of South Region - SAFE. Good stopping point.

properties.name: Ambam
properties.description: Border town. Last major Cameroonian town before Gabon.

properties.name: Kye-Ossi
properties.description: Cameroon-Gabon-Equatorial Guinea tripoint border. Take GABON crossing, NOT EQ Guinea.

properties.name: Bitam
properties.description: First town in Gabon - SAFE. Resupply point. Welcome to Gabon!

properties.name: Minvoul
properties.description: Gateway to Minkébé National Park region. Safe town.

properties.name: Otsala Kokowa NP Area
properties.description: Destination: Otsala Kokowa National Park area in northern Gabon. Remote but safe.
